gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Mavericks 125, Trail Blazers 112
gameRecap.excerpt: The Mavericks defeated the Trail Blazers, 125-112. Luka Doncic recorded 32 points, 10 assists, and 6 rebounds for the Mavericks, with Dante Exum (23 points, seven assists) and Tim Hardaway Jr. (20 points, four rebounds) combining for 43 points in the victory. Anfernee Simons tallied a season-high 30 points along with 8 assists and 5 rebounds for the Trail Blazers in the losing effort. The Mavericks improve to 13-8 in the regular season, while the Trail Blazers fall to 6-15.
